title: Astronaut Katherine Bennell-Pegg named Australian of the Year | 7NEWS
description: Katherine Bennell-Pegg, an astronaut from Adelaide who became the first Australian to qualify for space travel under the nation's flag in 2024, has been named Australian of the Year for 2026. Olympic champion Cathy Freeman received the nation's highest honour as a Companion of the Order of Australia. Other recipients include dementia researcher Harry Bredatti as Senior Australian of the Year, Indigenous employment advocate Frank Mitchell as Local Hero, and endurance runner Ned Brockman as Young Australian of the Year. title: Minneapolis erupts after second fatal ICE shooting | 7NEWS
description: Federal immigration agents shot and killed 37-year-old Alex Preti, a local ICU nurse in Minneapolis, after he attempted to help a woman pushed over by a Border Patrol agent. The incident, captured on video from multiple angles, shows Preti being wrestled to the ground and struck before being fatally shot, despite no evidence he reached for his legally permitted firearm. This marks the second fatal shooting by ICE agents in Minneapolis within weeks, following the death of local mother Renee Goode, prompting the state governor to demand the immediate withdrawal of 3,000 federal immigration agents from the city. title: 'It was murder': Resident reacts to fatal ICE shooting of Minneapolis nurse | 7NEWS | 7NEWS
description: Alex Pretti, a 37-year-old American ICU nurse, was fatally shot by federal immigration agents during an operation in Minneapolis. Video footage shows Pretti holding a phone and being pepper sprayed before being wrestled to the ground and shot, contradicting official claims he approached armed with intent to kill officers.   The incident has sparked mass protests and a political firestorm, with Minnesota's Governor calling the official account "lies" while President Trump defended the agents. title: 'She's blatantly lying': Anger at officials over fatal ICE shooting | 7NEWS
description: Thousands of protesters have gathered in Minneapolis to demand answers after ICE agents shot and killed Alex Pretti during an immigration enforcement operation.
